spring-controller-mappings - Spring Controller Mappings

USAGE:
    spring-controller-mappings

DESCRIPTION:
    Display Spring Boot controller mappings. Shows all @RequestMapping
    and HTTP method mappings (GET, POST, PUT) with file locations.

OUTPUT:
    Controller file, path, and HTTP method mappings

CONFIGURATION:
    -conf-dev-gawk PATH
        Path to GNU awk for pattern matching

EXAMPLES:
    spring-controller-mappings
